{"tid":1530862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新口號：「港鐵殺人，如同警黑。」","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:14:04.000Z","uid":153771,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a08b2ab7a0e87d92c4fe7008ab5bcb9fece5ba0","tid":1530862,"uid":153771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"黨鐵一定要清算，721之後，去到尋日901先搞黨鐵，香港人對黨鐵真係已經好撚善良。<br />\n<br />\n 721放黑社會入站，唔開車。<br />\n831放警察入站，唔開車。<br />\n封站，協助警察圍捕，等同送人去死，成為幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n放行警察入公共交通工具，危害市民安全。<br />\n<br />\n要求交出831當晚CCTV片段，還原真相，尋回失蹤義士。<br />\n<br />\n推上國際，要求國際對香港發出黑色旅遊警示，香港已經唔再安全。<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵唔交CCTV，唔回應，繼續同流合污，香港人，一定會令你成為第一個執笠嘅企業。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港鐵殺人，如同警黑</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"64a4d85bea456cbe41a4662547561fafb8cbdcb7","tid":1530862,"uid":153771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵殺人，如同警黑。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1696c643954733b57073df345d9abbc8c938a0b8","tid":1530862,"uid":153771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵殺人，如同警黑。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6831867f195074f2346ea224eb2c865a36295552","tid":1530862,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"[譴責破壞] 港鐵重建計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530623</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8286ffd1e73c73b27c806128d785f3493af3887d","tid":1530862,"uid":153771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵殺人，如同警黑。</span></span>"},{"pid":"e500f17e6e366f91397d93c432b0593e0649c823","tid":1530862,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2